    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"516\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/furInHoudini.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120575&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=516&amp;height=352\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643901/furInHoudini.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120575&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"619\" data-width=\"907\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643915\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"furInHoudini.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643901\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"de72e7c3-56b5-42b0-a0e8-d3d6da738559\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/furInHoudini.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120575&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=907&amp;height=619 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/furInHoudini.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120575&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=516&amp;height=352 1x\"></span><p /><p /><h2 id=\"FurandHairinHoudini-RenderFur\">Render Fur</h2><p>To render Houdini fur with RenderMan, we need to add the required RenderMan curve attributes and use the <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661553\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrMarschnerHair</a> hair Bxdf.</p><h2 id=\"FurandHairinHoudini-AddCurvesAttributes\">Add Curves Attributes</h2><p>Typically all you would need is a width attribute added as the default is rather...thick.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"272\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/rfh_curveWidth.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433121326&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=272&amp;height=248\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643901/rfh_curveWidth.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433121326&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"405\" data-width=\"443\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643957\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_curveWidth.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643901\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e19b7a05-cd4b-4dcf-a17a-5b6b2ea1559f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/rfh_curveWidth.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433121326&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=443&amp;height=405 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/rfh_curveWidth.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433121326&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=272&amp;height=248 1x\"></span><p>Set the width to the desired value and name it &quot;width&quot; for clarity.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"530\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/hairwidthattrib.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120993&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=530&amp;height=247\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643901/hairwidthattrib.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120993&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"442\" data-width=\"947\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643933\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"hairwidthattrib.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643901\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"cd7b154e-6e53-42fd-a1a5-08770ec8e98b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/hairwidthattrib.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120993&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=947&amp;height=442 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/hairwidthattrib.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120993&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=530&amp;height=247 1x\"></span><p /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-tip conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"4182441f-fd24-4d8e-9e72-583dcf68326f\" data-macro-name=\"tip\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-approve confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>For cubic<strong> bezier</strong> curve interpolation, we need to set the <strong>Guide Groom</strong> node's <strong>Guide Creation/Segments</strong> as a <strong>multiple of 3</strong>, e.g. 3, 6, 9, etc.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"550\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/groom_segments.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433121326&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=550&amp;height=248\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643901/groom_segments.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433121326&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"392\" data-width=\"866\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643951\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"groom_segments.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643901\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"4cddf67d-e1c7-4d15-97f6-5abe646082ec\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/groom_segments.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433121326&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=866&amp;height=392 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/groom_segments.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433121326&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=550&amp;height=248 1x\" /></span></div></div><p /><p>In the ROP, under Dicing, note the control for minimum hair width which sets the minimal width for the hair in pixels globally. Hair that is very thin may require more minimum samples in rendering to avoid aliasing or missed hair</p><h2 id=\"FurandHairinHoudini-CreateandAssigntheHairShader\">Create and Assign the Hair Shader</h2><p>Dive into the fur's shopnet. Create a PxrMaterialBuilder Network and PxrMarschnerHair inside the fur Network. </p><p /><p>Set the Material of the fur object to point to this shader path.</p><p>Note that we default to tube hair <em>unless</em> normals are supplied, then they become ribbons. Camera-facing/billboard curves are <em>not</em> available.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"442\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/furMarschnerHair.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120993&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=247\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643901/furMarschnerHair.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120993&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"401\" data-width=\"715\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643936\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"furMarschnerHair.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643901\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"27e4fde9-2a93-46f6-80d5-0de466a6e42d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/furMarschnerHair.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120993&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=715&amp;height=401 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/furMarschnerHair.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120993&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=247 1x\"></span><h2 id=\"FurandHairinHoudini-Display\">Display</h2><p>Turn off display for other nodes so only fur is displayed.</p><p /><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"612\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/furdisplaynode.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120836&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=612&amp;height=248\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544643901/furdisplaynode.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120836&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"410\" data-width=\"1011\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643927\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"furdisplaynode.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544643901\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"904c82a6-fd6a-4b39-9a0f-0ba9bb8f1bbb\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/furdisplaynode.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120836&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1011&amp;height=410 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544643901/furdisplaynode.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433120836&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=612&amp;height=248 1x\"></span><p /><h2 id=\"FurandHairinHoudini-Render!\">Render!</h2>"
    }
  },
